{"type": "article", "id": 16911, "title": "Jeremy Scott 的新款翅膀鞋", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-02T06:50:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000341XHsNMKB2DjFgZvqY.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t美国设计师 Jeremy Scott 的翅膀鞋尽管夸张大胆，却很受潮人欢迎。他最新为 adidas 设计的鞋子要收敛一些，以Superstar 为鞋型，翅膀缩小插在鞋的两侧，很可爱。翅膀上有些类似浮雕的处理，配上鞋身黑白相间的条纹，有了质感。是一双百搭而不失个性的鞋。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144151Pk0dJpNvCVt9LO6D.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144152qHRAVnpPe3Z5cQoJ.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144152Vbn1xB6yLvh8g0OH.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144153vtzMRFmKdY894nZp.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}